  "detailed_description": "<h1>Disclaimer</h1><p>The Struggles Of Stefan is currently intended to display best on horizontal monitors (landscape) and not vertical (portrait).</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A 2.5-dimensional platformer with a plot of accepting life choices, and their potential ramifications.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/6fdad2a45b6a925ada0fab52ea05a5f7.poster.avif?t=1754669242\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/6fdad2a45b6a925ada0fab52ea05a5f7.webm?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/6fdad2a45b6a925ada0fab52ea05a5f7.mp4?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Acquire particular items to accomplish each level quicker & easier.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/982cf697d8b2ee86eae723ed6d5e6955.poster.avif?t=1754669242\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/982cf697d8b2ee86eae723ed6d5e6955.webm?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/982cf697d8b2ee86eae723ed6d5e6955.mp4?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Basic controller mechanics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/d6c292a81b0d922d702459a2d4b18a8d.poster.avif?t=1754669242\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/d6c292a81b0d922d702459a2d4b18a8d.webm?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/d6c292a81b0d922d702459a2d4b18a8d.mp4?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Multiple chapters consisting of numerous themes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/bccb00a333416aef218804755483452b.poster.avif?t=1754669242\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/bccb00a333416aef218804755483452b.webm?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382020/extras/bccb00a333416aef218804755483452b.mp4?t=1754669242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
